msgctxt "sn46.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Cakkavattivagga "
msgstr "5. A Wheel Turning Monarch "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 45. Paññavantasutta → paññavasuttaṃ (bj) | paññavā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Paññavantasutta "
msgstr "45. Wise "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.45:1.1"
msgid "“‘Paññavā aneḷamūgo, paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti, bhante, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Sir they speak of a person who is ‘wise, no idiot’. "

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, ‘paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti? "
msgstr "How is a person who is wise, no idiot defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.45:1.3"
msgid "“Sattannaṃ kho, bhikkhu, bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“Mendicant, they’re called wise, no idiot because they’ve developed and cultivated the seven awakening factors. "

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.4"
msgid "Katamesaṃ sattannaṃ? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.5"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgassa … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgassa—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.45:1.6"
msgid "imesaṃ kho, bhikkhu, sattannaṃ bojjhaṅgānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā ‘paññavā aneḷamūgo’ti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "They’re called wise, no idiot because they’ve developed and cultivated these seven awakening factors.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.45:1.7"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

